{"tid":1145983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"綠軍應該放棄 Kyrie Irving ??","createTime":"2019-05-09T03:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T16:08:49.000Z","uid":189695,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"10dc4965d9b5715bdfe4be590f047159b2c4076c","tid":1145983,"uid":189695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>1. Irving 想做大佬</strong><br />\n當初離開LBJ都係想證明自己，但綠軍打法係團隊籃球，同球隊夾唔黎<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 帶隊能力差</strong><br />\n命中率今季好飄忽或者可以話係差<br />\n季初屌班後生仔，令到球隊氣氛唔好 <br />\nFirst Round 打冇Oladipo 既 Pacers 場場都贏唔過雙位數<br />\nLBJ回歸騎士之前，佢帶騎士都係下遊球隊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 綠軍團隊打法</strong><br />\n教練Stevens 打法係團隊打法，上季唔齊腳下化學作用好好，打到入東決<br />\n今季Irving 同 Hayward 復出，但戰續反而唔理想<br />\n<br />\n<strong>綠軍</strong><br />\n一係今季簽多粒星 (AD) 同配合Irving，如果唔係好難再行前<br />\n一係交易Irving，換返其他一線或者二線頭既球員，況且而家有 Tatum, Brown, Rozier, Horford, Hayward<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Irving</strong><br />\n去 LAC/ NYK再組過隊做返二佬會比較好"},{"pid":"8c683142180aa794adde0037a68130556eab8038","tid":1145983,"uid":124268,"like":10,"dislike":16,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"如果佢肯走直頭係雙贏,Terry Rozier值得打正選"},{"pid":"04b123018d6ebdabc6c96d5ae357398fd06cbd64","tid":1145983,"uid":229886,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"去lakers幫占士拎翻個冠啦"},{"pid":"4d02adaac51c61b2eb7976623c5d28f368fcdbd4","tid":1145983,"uid":170772,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"同kd一齊去ny啦"},{"pid":"1486ff79b86dd1d48431f3e8d15c7c635c9ea0fc","tid":1145983,"uid":174418,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"藍球員體能 技術競爭激烈 <br />\n<br />\n狀態唔夠好 就要落選"},{"pid":"fb606421c736c8cb8548411cadd2d5bd66f1a3bd","tid":1145983,"uid":555,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"8c683142180aa794adde0037a68130556eab8038","tid":1145983,"uid":124268,"like":10,"dislike":16,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:2